column2: SELECT     s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.z, s.zwarning,     g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err,     g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err FROM    GalSpecLine AS g    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE     h_alpha_flux > h_alpha_flux_err*#     AND h_beta_flux > h_beta_flux_err*#     AND h_beta_flux_err > #     AND h_alpha_flux > #.*h_beta_flux     AND s.class = &&&     AND s.zwarning = #
